I"Ñ<p>Say you want to sort by some column in a datatable. Sample code below is from <a href="https://github.com/rtanglao/2016-r-rtgram/blob/master/colourname-void-square-piechart-from-csv.R">colourname-void-square-piechart-from-csv.R</a>. Note the hilarious <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">,]</code> which makes me laugh whenever I encounter it. Not a disrespectful laugh but a this is not the ‚ÄúC/C++/ruby/python/php syntax‚Äù you are looking for laugh :-) !</p>

